01:58:34.126 --> 01:58:34.426
So,

1961
01:58:35.446 --> 01:58:38.626
getting back to this framework for this session that there's two dominant types of

1962
01:58:38.706 --> 01:58:42.546
MRD in solid tumors, the first being MRD after systemic therapy in

1963
01:58:42.566 --> 01:58:44.826
